[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     898[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                               language: str) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     899[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """Build response for a screening action that did not pass."""
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     900[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     action = screening_result["action"]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     901[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     902[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     if action == "crisis_response":
