[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2737[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2738[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `screen_output(session_id, response, tool_call_history)`. The standard output checks (scope filter, hallucination check, vendor-managed guardrails) carry forward from recipe 11.1. The new check verifies that any "your appointment is confirmed" claim in the response is supported by an actual successful booking-tool result.*
