[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2897[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `close_conversation_and_archive(session_id, reason)`. Every conversation produces three durable artifacts: the conversation log (utterances, redacted of inadvertent PHI, with model and prompt versions stamped), the tool-call ledger (every tool invoked with arguments, results, and latency), and the booking-event journal entries (durable records for every successful booking, reschedule, or cancellation).*
